HEADWORD: Scrambler
<hw>Scram"bler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
scrambles; one who climbs on all fours.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A greedy and unceremonious contestant.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scrambling</ent>⟦br⟧
